Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.88,0:00:06.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoron☆小鶴屋學姐  第十一話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:06.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.70,0:00:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.02,0:00:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也好有型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的考試  我忘記寫名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  我也忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定是想騙取阿虛的共鳴來增加好感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  把試卷還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.66,0:00:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把名字抹掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼莫名其妙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.16,0:00:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我打完分再說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.89,0:00:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試卷還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.14,0:00:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師幫我把名字抹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:41.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿虛  我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.41,0:00:43.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我名字寫過了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.78,0:00:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你明天要補考
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoron～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:52.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.55,0:00:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（問15.請說明波線部太郎的心情）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（Nyoron）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.40,0:01:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（問3.請在四方格中填入恰當的詞語）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（那個不行）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:14.38,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（應該填緊急）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:18.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（煙熏奶酪）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoreron～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.25,0:01:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得這還不算最終答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.66,0:01:29.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣就滿意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:35.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（無法認同的心情）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（問9.寫出水的構造式）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:45.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（真好啊!）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:51.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新的情報了記得更新  我的後援
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.73,0:01:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我沒空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  手不受控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:57.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}（鹹菜  98日元）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫完啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.32,0:02:02.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朝倉寫得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.42,0:02:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鶴屋你寫得怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.38,0:02:08.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoron～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫完了就回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼會  阿虛和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題裡出現了熏酪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要加油
